comment: Matthews (DAL) makes contact with Anderson's (NOP) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Gordon (NOP) makes incidental contact with Nowitzki (DAL) that does not affect his FOM.
Nowitzki (DAL) sets the screen on Cole (NOP) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Pachulia (DAL) and Gordon (NOP) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Anderson (NOP) splits his feet on the perimeter as he makes his move.
Pachulia (DAL) legally contests Anderson's (NOP) shot attempt.
Gordon (NOP) does not intentionally kick the ball on the play.
Nowitzki (DAL) and Davis (NOP) make incidental contact with one another on the perimeter.
Cole (NOP) sets the screen on Barea (DAL) and continues to hold him after setting the screen.
Holiday (NOP) makes incidental contact with Barea (DAL) as he drives to the basket.
Holiday (NOP) legally contests Matthews' (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Nowitzki (DAL) commits a take foul on Cole (NOP).
